replies.body:
{{champion:38}} {{champion:127}} 

Kennen and Akali are Energy based.

And it's entirely possible to go out of mana if you mess up a combo. Also, the 1.5 maximum mana just isn't good, Even with a tear you get 40 ish mana back per E KILL, not cast. Depending on your lane rival, they can eat up a lot of E's before going down and on top of that Q costs 40 mana so the return is basically null.
